Ray Ross s/b Roy Ross.

<b>Roy Ross</b> opened a dance studio in Sarasota in 1949.  He was a featured dancer in several hit shows on Broadway.  He was also a friend of Joe and Lois Steinmetz. [<a href="http://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=1755&amp;dat=19490119&amp;id=D7cqAAAAIBAJ&amp;sjid=qGQEAAAAIBAJ&amp;pg=6151,4551977" rel="nofollow">1</a>] [<a href="http://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=1755&amp;dat=19490116&amp;id=DLcqAAAAIBAJ&amp;sjid=qGQEAAAAIBAJ&amp;pg=1712,4169153" rel="nofollow">2</a>] [<a href="http://fultonhistory.com/Newspaper 18/Rhinebeck NY Gazette/Rhinebeck NY Gazette 1947-1949/Rhinebeck NY Gazette 1947-1949 - 0944.pdf" rel="nofollow">3</a>] [<a href="http://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=1755&amp;dat=19490118&amp;id=DrcqAAAAIBAJ&amp;sjid=qGQEAAAAIBAJ&amp;pg=3570,4443544" rel="nofollow">4</a>]
